      <problem>
        <statement>
          <p>
            Give an example of a pair <m>(G,\cdot)</m> that satisfies axioms 1 and 2 of <xref ref="def-group" /> and an element of <m>G</m> that has a <em>left</em> inverse but not a <em>right</em> inverse.
          </p>
        </statement>
        <solution>
          <p>

